title: La Veneta
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Italian restaurant offering some vegan choices. At breakfast, avocado on sourdough the with tomato and quinoa, fruit loaf with jam, fruit smoothie, sourdough toast with jam. At lunch, bruschetta with choice of toppings, the La Veneta linguine, antipasto of breads, vegetables & crackers with grilled polenta, pizza with napoli and veggies. At dinner, several tapas (olives, mixed salad, seasoned vegetables, pear walnut salad), La Veneta liguine. For dessert, a lemon sorbet with fresh fruit.
